tr.td: US Flag with 49 stars. In use 4 July 1959–3 July 1960. It was defined in Executive Order 10798.
created by Gunter Küchler / Berlin using Inkscape
Flag design by the U.S. Government; SVG created by jacobolus using Adobe Illustrator, and released into the public domain
